powerdown: powerdown  Control scripts for the unRAID server Environment.
powerdown:
powerdown: Adds /sbin/powerdown script to assist with quick unRAID poweroff
powerdown:
powerdown: Install Variable options:
powerdown: CTRLALTDEL=yes set ctrl-alt-del to do powerdown instead of reboot
powerdown: SYSLOG=YES     do initial syslog saving upon installation
powerdown: STATUS=YES     Show status upon installation
powerdown: START=YES      do initial start upon installation
powerdown: 
powerdown: Install with VAR's as defined above like:
powerdown: VAR=YES OTHERVAR=YES installpkg powerdown-1.02-noarch-unRAID.tgz
powerdown: Like Like: 
powerdown: CTRLALTDEL=yes installpkg powerdown-1.02-noarch-unRAID.tgz
powerdown: 
powerdown: /etc/rc.d/rc.unRAID script has basic pre-power down functions
powerdown: Hooks are placed in /etc/rc.d/rc.local_shutdown
powerdown: to allow ormal poweroff/shutdown commands do a graceful shutdown
powerdown: 
powerdown: Diagnostic mode for quick syslog dump/save to /boot/logs
powerdown: call as /etc/rc.d/rc.unRAID syslog 
